{"tid":1854292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓國武漢肺炎確診第11宗，另首現境內傳染","createTime":"2020-01-31T11:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T12:38:15.000Z","uid":161430,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"34b0c3ff2e0cf07612bd2ea1edfdaff1481bab22","tid":1854292,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"韓國新型冠狀病毒肺炎個案再增加，今日（31日）截至下午，中央應急處置本部公布新增5宗確診病例，累計11宗。<br />\n<br />\n而今早從武漢飛抵首爾的首架運載國民政府包機，機上368名公民中有18人出現發燒徵狀，抵達後已被送院。韓聯社報道，機上其中12人在武漢天河機場登機前接受檢疫時已出現徵狀，另有6人抵達首爾金浦機場後出現徵狀。其餘沒有徵狀的350人，按原定計劃乘坐政府安排的車輛前往隔離設施，隔離兩星期。另有一人在武漢因體溫過高未獲准登機。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，第6例患者是韓國首位武漢肺炎交叉感染病例，他接觸過的第3例患者20日從武漢「無症狀」入境韓國後在社區自由活動數天，25日才被隔離，26日確診感染。"},{"pid":"3381ee3fa483c79fbe69d38e18943d3f3e330fd4","tid":1854292,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"校長呀校長，你哋放過老師啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1853605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1853605</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a0d4e1d8355c25503aa6c847475af5d1ddeac2f0","tid":1854292,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"PIN THIS 簽呀！香港普選PETITION by SOLOMON<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=191fde6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a><br />\n最後一日！唔做就洩！"},{"pid":"a226aada2c9fd4d5667358ddadd0e165c3f3d459","tid":1854292,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:50:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武肺背後嘅第三次世界大戰：諜戰丶生化戰丶經濟戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854117</a><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b